cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a new method for interpretable machine learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method involves selecting key features, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the importance of fidelity in the evaluation of the method, which is a concern in computer security (cs.CR).
